thread.title: Mr Ian Johnston
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Mr Ian Johnston

author: Mr Ian Johnston
title: Mr Ian Johnston
text:
Needing a car for a week in Auckland, we approached one of the big companies, naturally enough. It could not promise the make of car, gave a high price and offered a ridiculous cost of damage waiver. Omega was brilliant!
p.s. I am neither an employee of Omega nor a relative of one.
